author: A_Brickset_user
title: Cool Graphics!
review: I HIGHLY reccomend this piece of software to ANYONE who reads this message! This is really cool graphics and fun, fast and furious game we're talkin' about! Choose what zone you want to go on, pick a car and a colour for that car, and race, race, race, race, race, race! YOU MUST GET THIS GAME WHILE YOU STILL CAN!!!!! (I was surprised I found it when I did!)
